     C                     MOVELLAZAIS    LBZAIS
     C                     Z-ADDLAZAIK    LBZAIK
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     LBODHZ
     C                     Z-ADD0         LBKANY
     C                     Z-ADD0         LBKANM
     C                     Z-ADD0         LBKAND
     C                     Z-ADD0         LBSPYY
     C                     Z-ADD0         LBSPMM
